abstract: Stocks close at highest level of year in wake of comments made by Federal Reserve chairwoman Janet L Yellen about strength of economy and Fed's commitment to slow increase in interest rates.
lead_paragraph: Apple and Microsoft led tech stocks higher, while energy companies fell along with the price of oil.

headline.main: Yellen’s Remarks Move Market to Year’s Highest Point
